  "text": "Generation of cAMP was assayed in serum-free medium containing 1 mmol/L 3-isobutyl-1-methylxanthine (IBMX) in the presence of propranolol or isoproterenol (ISO) with 100 mol/L ascorbic acid as indicated for 20 minutes as previously described [CITATION_1] using a cAMP immunoassay (R&D Systems).",
